com.hazelcast.client.config

Class ClientProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.instance.HazelcastProperties
      • com.hazelcast.client.config.ClientProperties

  • public class ClientProperties
extends HazelcastProperties
    Container for configured Hazelcast Client properties (ClientProperty).

    A ClientProperty can be set as:

    • an environmental variable using System.setProperty(String, String)
    • the programmatic configuration using Config.setProperty(String, String)
    • the XML configuration http://docs.hazelcast.org/docs/latest-dev/manual/html-single/hazelcast-documentation.html#system-properties

    The old property definitions are deprecated since Hazelcast 3.6. Please use the new ClientProperty definitions instead.

        Parameters:
